==Introduction==
20.3cm連装砲のマイナーバージョンアップ版、それが同2号連装砲です。<br />
元々優秀な重巡洋艦用主砲を改良して、主に妙高型などに搭載されました。<br />
初期主砲搭載の他の重巡達も、近代化改装時に順次本砲に換装されていきました。

''The no.2 twin gun is a slightly upgraded version of the 20.3cm twin gun.''<br>
''The excellent heavy cruiser main guns were upgraded and used as the main guns of the Myoukou-class.''<br>
''Other heavy cruisers had their early-model guns eventually replaced with this one during their modernisations.''

